Well Im very sad I know that man4l is with the "HOE" I checked her telephone messages and he was on there and he said that he loved her I dont know what to think at this point yesterday I called her 31 times and said nothing I was so pissed and I still am today is fathers day and Im tired of playing happy family so I decided to come in the house and edit my journal. I love him but im starting to feel like he doesnt love me anymore I just dont know what to do should I stay should I leave well technically we arent an item but we still talk so I still feel as though Im his girl you know when you are crazy inlove you  do some crazy shit. Theres is this other guy that is kind of cute at my church and i think he likes me too but im not sure I think Im gonna talk to him for a while and try to stop caring about man 4l so much hes taking up too much of my time ya kno'. On a lighter side Im suppose to be getting a new car a sunfire I think but my mom says she wants me to have something bigger whatever that means! But it wont matter I just hope whatever it is I will have it before my birthday so I can cruse in my new car. To my friends you know who you are i miss you guys already me me, erica,kmg, mel, tee, cambrey (hows life?) I love you all hope ur having a safe summer so far to me me, dont worry abouthim its normal but if you start to care you will end up just like me sad and lonely wondering where he is all he time and shit and do trust that is not a good feeling. Hes been yours all this time trust me his ass aint going nowhere nowand if he doess his loss not yours so have fun just having a man to call yours. until next time THE REALIST OF THEM ALL!!!!!!!! TTYL THE REALIST!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Man my heart is really catching hell this guy I'll call CS26 that I use to talk to has moved on and left me behind. I brought it all on myself though and I really can't blame him for it. CS26 went to church with me on one sunday and my boyfriend was there so to avoid looking as though I was cheating I went and talked to my boyfriend instead of sitting with him. I knew it was bold and after the fat i felt bad about it. Them I asked and he said that it didn't bother him but I knew he wasn't being honest. I really like him and now I don't even have him anymore and I don't think that he really cares. So now he's talking to this girl who is sheisty because she talked all that time about how me and boy CS26 looked so cute together and now shes talking to him. What a BITCH!!! same damn thing I said. But I don't even know what it is, its like I just grew so attached to him he did everything I asked, kisses hugs, and all the affection that I never had in a relationship. I was so ready to be with him as a couple. I guess it just wasnt meant to be. its like every guy I try to talk to I fuck it up some how. But I never thought that if he did find out that it would even matter since we werent together. Im scared to talk to him I dont know whaat hes going to say or do and I want him to be honest but I dont think that he would. He'll try to hoe me or end up never talking to me agian.Ok well thats enough of that!! Then there is my biggest crush and he still is. I want him so bad but he has a girlfriend. Right same thing I said FUCK HIS GIRL I WANT HIM!!!! But thats not the case I want him to leave her and I want him to be with me. He wants me and I know it but he loves her and love can do some awfully crazy stuff. Trust me I know That If I dont know anything else. I think that Im going to tell him that. I think abotu him no matter what I do I tried to make him jealous of boy CS26 but it didnt work. I just like him so much and I dont know what to do with myself. But you know CS26 Im really missing him right now and I just cant control it I just want to palm him face and kiss him until he cant stand it anymore and gives in and takes me in the bathroom and does exactly what he wants with me. YA'LL JUST DONT KNOW!!!!! I dont know what Im going to do until next time.
   YOU'LL NEED ME BEFORE I'LL NEED YOU!!! CHOW!!!!!!!!

Hello people this is one of the realist people you will ever find.Thanks to those viewing my first entry.Shiesty is at the top because females are just that. You never know when you come across a real one. Let me tell you my situation, this kid which will always remain nameless I'll call her Jane Doe. she lied on me to this guy then tried to blame it on someone else. Not only that because that is beside the true point of this story. She also fucked over some of her other friends. then she expects us to be cool. Hell no I think  that i have suffered long enough, and our friendship is long over due. So now she is mad because I don't talk to her anymore. but everything she is going through she did to herself. It might sound heartless but I don't even care at this point. She is always depressed and sad and I don't need that in my life because I am on my way to college and i don't need anyone else's drama in my life when I'm dealing with my own. I don't even think that she knows  that she hurt me and I'm upset as hell but I don't stress about it because I don't want to be depressed because my friend betrayed me oe the 3rd time since I have known her but as I always say this too shall pass. !!!!!!!until next time!!!!!!!!
